es><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property><Property><Name>c++_compatible</Name></Property><Property><Name>TcDependOnClassFactory</Name><Value>TcIotDrivers</Value></Property><Property><Name>no_explicit_call</Name><Value>do not call this POU directly</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>ST_MqttConfig</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
============================================================
ST_MqttConfig
============================================================
PURPOSE
  MQTT broker connection and topic configuration.
  Populated from GVL_Config defaults on startup.
  Operator can override all fields from the HMI MQTT-Config
  panel, then press "Apply & Reconnect" to activate changes.

NOTES
  • Changing any field requires pressing Apply (triggers bApplyConfig
    rising edge in FB_MqttManager) to reconnect with new settings.
  • Use TLS (bUseTls = TRUE, nPort = 8883) for production deployments.
  • Credentials are NOT stored in persistent memory — they must be
    re-entered after a cold restart unless the HMI retains them.
============================================================
]]></Comment><BitSize>6336</BitSize><SubItem><Name>sBrokerAddress</Name><Type>STRING(255)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ IP or hostname of MQTT broker     ]]></Comment><BitSize>2048</BitSize><BitOffs>0</BitOffs><Default><String>imsiot.aws.thinger.io</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>nPort</Name><Type>UINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ 1883 = plain, 8883 = TLS/SSL      ]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><BitOffs>2048</BitOffs><Default><Value>1883</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>sClientId</Name><Type>STRING(64)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Must be unique per broker   ]]></Comment><BitSize>520</BitSize><BitOffs>2064</BitOffs><Default><String>Beckhoff</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>sUsername</Name><Type>STRING(64)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Leave empty if no auth required   ]]></Comment><BitSize>520</BitSize><BitOffs>2584</BitOffs><Default><String>ims_iot</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>sPassword</Name><Type>STRING(64)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Leave empty if no auth required   ]]></Comment><BitSize>520</BitSize><BitOffs>3104</BitOffs><Default><String>123456789</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>bUseTls</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE enables TLS/SSL connection   ]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>3624</BitOffs><Default><Bool>false</Bool></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>sTopicPrefix</Name><Type>STRING(64)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Base prefix for all topics        ]]></Comment><BitSize>520</BitSize><BitOffs>3632</BitOffs><Default><String>irrigation</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>sMainTopic</Name><Type>STRING(128)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Full publish topic            ]]></Comment><BitSize>1032</BitSize><BitOffs>4152</BitOffs><Default><String>irrigation/status</String></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>SubscribeTopic</Name><Type>STRING(128)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Full subscribe topic          ]]></Comment><BitSize>1032</BitSize><BitOffs>5184</BitOffs><Default><String>irrigation/command</String></Default>