============================================================
METHOD: BuildStatusJson
============================================================
PURPOSE
  Assembles the outgoing JSON status payload from current
  system data stored in VAR_INPUT. Writes result into
  sJsonStatusPayload (VAR_OUTPUT).

OUTPUT FORMAT EXAMPLE
  {"timestamp":"2026-04-28 12:00:00",
   "valve_1_setpoint":50.0,"valve_1_actual":49.8,"valve_1_source":"HMI",
   "valve_2_setpoint":25.0,"valve_2_actual":25.1,"valve_2_source":"MQTT",
   "valve_3_setpoint":75.0,"valve_3_actual":74.9,"valve_3_source":"HMI",
   "temperature_c":22.5,"water_level_pct":65.3,"water_level_mm":653.0}
============================================================
]]></Comment><Local><Name>sTemp</Name><Type>STRING(2048)</Type><BitSize>16392</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>GetClientRef</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
