 an FB call's parameter list. Populate these arrays each
 cycle, then pass them in a single assignment.]]></Comment><BitSize>96</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">aValveActual</Name><Type>REAL</Type><ArrayInfo><LBound>1</LBound><Elements>3</Elements></ArrayInfo><BitSize>96</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">aValveSource</Name><Type>STRING(8)</Type><ArrayInfo><LBound>1</LBound><Elements>3</Elements></ArrayInfo><BitSize>216</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">fbValve1</Name><Type>FB_ValveControl</Type><Comment><![CDATA[///Not Implemented currently]]></Comment><BitSize>36224</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">fbValve2</Name><Type>FB_ValveControl</Type><BitSize>36224</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">fbValve3</Name><Type>FB_ValveControl</Type><BitSize>36224</BitSize></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>TwinCAT_PreventOnlineChangeGvl</Name><SubItem><Name Static="true">WriteLineIDs</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><Default><Bool>false</Bool></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">PlcProfilerActive</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><Default><Bool>false</Bool></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">PlcProfilerConfigChecksum</Name><Type>STRING(64)</Type><BitSize>520</BitSize><Default><String /></Default></SubItem><Properties><Property><Name>linkalways</Name></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>GVL_IO</Name><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_L1V11</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I* // Water Level Sensors]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_L1V20</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">bTop_position_1</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>TcDataArea</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">bBottom_position_1</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>TcDataArea</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_L2V21</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_Tmp_1</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_Tmp_2</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_PosFeedback_1</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I* //Position feedback from the encoder]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_PosFeedback_2</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AI_PosFeedback_3</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ AT %I*]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>-999</Value></Default></SubItem><Properties><Property><Name>qualified_only</Name></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>GVL_System</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
============================================================
GVL_System  —  Runtime shared state
============================================================
PURPOSE
  Central runtime data bus. Written by function blocks,
  read by MAIN and mirrored to GVL_HMI for display.

OWNERSHIP
  Valve[1..3]     → written by FB_ValveControl instances
  Sensors         → written by FB_SensorIO
  CSV_*           → written by FB_CSVLogger
  MQTT_*          → written by FB_MqttManager
  SystemReady,
  AnyFaultActive  → computed in MAIN
============================================================
]]></Comment><SubItem><Name Static="true">CSV_FileError</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ File I/O error flag]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_Connected</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE when broker connection is active]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">CSV_LastWriteTime</Name><Type>DATE_AND_TIME</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Timestamp of last successful row write]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">Valve</Name><Type>ST_ValveData</Type><ArrayInfo><LBound>1</LBound><Elements>3</Elements></ArrayInfo><Comment><![CDATA[ Index 1=V1, 2=V2, 3=V3]]></Comment><BitSize>1152</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">Sensors</Name><Type>ST_SensorData</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ ── Sensor data (written by FB_SensorIO) ─────────────────────]]></Comment><BitSize>416</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">CSV_RowsWritten</Name><Type>UDINT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Total rows written this session]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">CSV_CurrentFile</Name><Type>STRING(80)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Active filename (e.g. IrrigationLog_2026-04.csv)]]></Comment><BitSize>648</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_Error</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE on connection error or reconnect]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">CSV_LoggerState</Name><Type>E_CSVLogState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Internal state for diagnostics]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_LastErrorCode</Name><Type GUID="{18071995-0000-0000-0000-000000000019}">HRESULT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HRESULT error code (0 = OK)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_LastErrorMsg</Name><Type>STRING(128)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Human-readable error description]]></Comment><BitSize>1032</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_LastRxTopic</Name><Type>STRING(255)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Last received topic]]></Comment><BitSize>2048</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_LastRxPayload</Name><Type>STRING(2048)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Last received payload (for diagnostics)]]></Comment><BitSize>16392</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_LastJsonStatus</Name><Type>STRING(2048)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Last outgoing JSON payload (for diagnostics)]]></Comment><BitSize>16392</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">MQTT_NewCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE for one cycle after valid command received]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">SystemReady</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ All valves homed and no active faults]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AnyFaultActive</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ OR of all valve IsFault flags]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">AnySensorFault</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE if any sensor is disconnected/faulty]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem></DataType><DataType><Name>GVL_Config</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
============================================================
GVL_Config  —  System-wide compile-time constants
============================================================
All values here are CONSTANT and cannot be changed at runtime.
To change a value: edit here, rebuild and download the project.
Runtime-adjustable parameters are exposed via GVL_HMI.

CALIBRATION REQUIRED:
  • VALVE_FULL_STROKE_MM  — measure physical travel of each actuator
  • WATER_LEVEL_ENG_MAX_MM — measure the full-scale tank height
  • Sensor raw min/max    — verify with your specific EL3074 settings
============================================================
]]></Comment><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_FULL_STROKE_MM</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm — full travel (3600° stepper)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><Default><Value>6.096</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_POSITION_TOLERANCE</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ %  — in-position dead-band]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><Default><Value>0.5</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_MOVE_VELOCITY</Name><Type>LREAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm/s — max travel speed]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><Default><Value>1.5</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_MOVE_ACCELERATION</Name><Type>LREAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm/s² — ramp-up rate]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><Default><Value>16.9085</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_MOVE_DECELERATION</Name><Type>LREAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm/s² — ramp-down rate]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><Default><Value>16.9085</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_MOVE_JERK</Name><Type>LREAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm/s³ — 0.0 = trapezoidal profile]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><Default><Value>53.5391</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">VALVE_HOMING_VELOCITY</Name><Type>LREAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm/s — slow speed during homing]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><Default><Value>1</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">WATER_LEVEL_RAW_MIN</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ ADC count at 0 % / 0 mm]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>0</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">WATER_LEVEL_RAW_MAX</Name><Type>INT</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ ADC count at 100 % / ENG_MAX_MM]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize><Default><Value>32767</Value></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">WATER_LEVEL_ENG_MIN_MM</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ mm at raw minimum]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><Default><Value>0</Value><