============================================================
GVL_HMI  —  HMI ↔ PLC interface layer
============================================================
PURPOSE
  All variables in this GVL are bound to TcHMI controls via
  the ADS symbol server. HMI_* variables are written by the
  operator (HMI inputs). ACT_* variables are written by the
  PLC (HMI outputs / displays).

NAMING CONVENTION
  HMI_*   → HMI writes, PLC reads  (operator commands)
  ACT_*   → PLC writes, HMI reads  (status displays)

BINDING PATTERN (TcHMI)
  %s%ADS.PLC1.GVL_HMI.<VariableName>%/s%
============================================================
]]></Comment><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve1_Reset</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI button: reset fault for valve 1]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve1_Stop</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI button: halt valve 1 movement]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve1_Homing</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI button: trigger re-homing valve 1]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve1_MQTT_Enable</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI checkbox: allow MQTT to command valve 1]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve1_Setpoint</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI input:  desired position 0–100 %]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_UPDATE</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI button: apply setpoint(s)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">ACT_Valve1_Fault</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PLC output: fault active flag]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">ACT_Valve1_State</Name><Type>E_ValveState</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PLC output: current state machine state]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">ACT_Valve1_Position</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PLC output: actual position 0–100 %]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">ACT_Valve1_Source</Name><Type>E_ValveSource</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PLC output: last command source enum]]></Comment><BitSize>16</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">ACT_Valve1_SourceText</Name><Type>STRING(8)</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PLC output: 'HMI', 'MQTT', or 'NONE']]></Comment><BitSize>72</BitSize></SubItem><SubItem><Name Static="true">HMI_Valve2_Reset</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ HMI button: reset fault for val